Hello Trust Wallet team,

Unfortunately, that PR was closed due to inactivity before it was merged. I have now resubmitted the token under a new PR #31643.

According to your official documentation, a second payment is not required if the asset was already accepted before. Since my token was already approved (but not merged), I kindly request you to transfer the paid fee from PR #31328 to PR #31643, so the new request can proceed.

Thank you very much for your support and clarification.

Best regards,
